    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an exceptional, collector-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, preserved in its original factory configuration. This A80 generation icon features the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, utilizing its sequential twin-turbocharger setup to deliver a linear power band and robust torque. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, offering precise gate engagement and seamless synchromesh operation. The chassis retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen helical limited-slip differential, ensuring peak lateral grip and predictable corner-exit dynamics. All body panels bear matching VIN tags, confirming a history free of structural compromise. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of corrosion or fluid seepage from the rear main seal or valve cover gaskets. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically pristine example of JDM engineering history.",
